{
  "stem": "26699.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, I wasn't considered eligible for the Army any more, in spite of being an officer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was thrown out from my job, where only government jobs exist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I stayed unemployed for about six months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only thing that I could do was to learn bridge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my activity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eventually, they released the tough regulations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was allowed to get a job as a civil engineer in a place where nobody wanted to go, somewhere close to the border.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But not having any choice, I had to accept it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I went there, and I worked, but with a feeling of being under punishment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I applied time and again to get a passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was impossible to get one, because they let out of the country, generally, people without professions, or very old, who were a burden for the country.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But young people, like me, and with a good profession, they wouldn't let out, by any means.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was paid a fraction of the salary of one who didn't apply for immigration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was given the most menial engineering jobs possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I knew that I did this on purpose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I knew that I took the chance on my own, so I didn't complain about all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After a couple of years, in 1961, I managed to get a job, also not so well-paid, below the average in Bucharest, in a design office, government design office, where I worked until 1969.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And now, if people remember, in 1968, it happened in Czechoslovakia what was called The Springs of Prague, when the Dubcek took command and tried to liberalize Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Between Springs and August, the Russians who didn't accept this sort of liberalization prepared to stop this movement.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
